<h1>About HabitWorkbench</h1>

<div style="max-width:900px;">

    <p>
        HabitWorkbench is a private, local-first desktop tool for designing and improving routines and habits.
        It’s inspired by the habit-building ideas and frameworks popularized by <b>James Clear</b>.
    </p>

    <h3>Credit & Inspiration</h3>

    <p>
        This app is influenced by concepts such as identity-based habits, habit shaping, environment design,
        and continuous improvement as discussed in James Clear’s work.
    </p>

